						<additions>
							<p>
								<name type="person" role="owner">Daṿid Leṿi Bar᾿am Ibn Mordekhai Leṿi Bar᾿am</name>: inscribed, folios 8r, 79v, 80v and 117r.</p>
							<p>Folio 3r-7r: a letter, dated <name type="place">Algiers</name>, <date calendar="Hebrew">25 Nisan [5]570</date> (<date calendar="Gregorian">1810</date>), sent by Daṿid Leṿi Bar᾿am to his brother, Ḥayim; Oriental cursive script.</p>
